POWER BI DENEB - COMPLETE ONE-SHEET DASHBOARD

DATA SOURCE
Import: AIA PowerBI One Sheet Database.xlsx
Select sheet: PowerBI_Data

ADD THESE FIELDS TO THE DENEB DATASET
- Company
- ProductName
- IndexName
- Currency
- CohortNo
- CohortStartDate
- CohortEndDate
- IndexBaseValue
- ParticipationRate
- CapRate
- FloorRate
- Date
- Price

POWER BI STEPS
1. Home > Get data > Excel workbook.
2. Open AIA PowerBI One Sheet Database.xlsx.
3. Select PowerBI_Data and choose Load.
4. Add the Deneb custom visual to the report canvas.
5. Drag the 13 fields listed above from PowerBI_Data into Deneb Values.
6. In Deneb, choose Create new specification > Vega-Lite > Empty.
7. Delete the sample JSON and paste the complete JSON below.
8. Choose Apply.

REAL FILTER BOXES
Add Power BI slicers outside Deneb using:
- Company
- ProductName
- CohortNo
- IndexName

The boxes drawn inside Deneb match the requested dashboard appearance. Use the Power BI slicers above for clickable filtering.

